### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@clientToken = CLIENT_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Accepter un devis (cas nominal - client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/accept-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here",
  "contract_content": "Contenu personnalisé du contrat"
}

### Test 2 - Accepter un devis sans contenu personnalisé
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/accept-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here"
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: quote_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/accept-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 4 - Erreur: devis déjà accepté
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/accept-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "already-accepted-quote-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: devis expiré
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/accept-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "expired-quote-uuid"
}

### Test 6 - Erreur: accès non autorisé
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/accept-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "other-client-quote-uuid"
}

